quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,123,"Allaahu on yamirii gom…óim…ìe …ìen ha…ìugol heefer…ìe …ìen sabu ko…ìe sabimbinta kon bonande e gom…óim…ìe …ìen tawde hi…ìe …ìadondiri. O yamiri …ìe kadi fe√±√±ingol doole e tii…óere fii hul…ìingol …ìeya sabu bone ma…ì…ìe. Alla ko wonndir…óo e gom…óum…ìe …ìen ballal e faabo Makko."
  9,124,"Si Alla jippinii cortewol e Nulaa…óo Makko on Muhammadu (yo o his), hino e naafiqii…ìe …ìen on lanndoray…óo jalkitugol o wi'a : "Ko hommbo e moo…óon woni ko ngol cortewol jippiingol e Muhammadu …ìeydi gom…óinal?" Ammaa …ìen gom…óim…ìe Alla …ìe goongini Nulaa…óo Makko on, gom…óii jippagol ngol cortewol …ìeydii …ìe gom…óinal e hoore gom…óinal ma…ì…ìe adinoo ngal, e hoore ko …ìe weltorii…ìe ko wahyu on jippini kon tawde nafa ma…ì…ìe aduna e laakara no e mun."
  9,125,"Ammaa non naafiqii…ìe …ìen, ko Alqur'aana jippoda-ta kon e √±aawooje maa fillayee, …óum ko √±awu e so…ìe …ìeydata …ìe sabu ko …ìe fenni ko jippini kon. √ëawu …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen …ìeydora jippagol Alkuran tawde tuma kala go…ó…óum jippii, …ìe wullitoto …óum, …ìe maayidiri non e keeferaaku."
  9,126,"E …ìee naafiqii…ìe yi'aali …ìe waajitora ko Alla jarribori …ìe kon huncugol fiyaaku ma…ì…ìe wirta naafiqaaku ma…ì…ìe hitaande kala laawol maa laa…ìi …ói…ói? Refti hoore ko …ìe anndi kon …óum ko Alla wa…ói, …ìe tuubatantaa Mo e keeferaaku ma…ì…ìe ngun, wanaa kam…ìe kadi woni …ìoorotoo…ìe e naafiqaaku ma…ì…ìe, wanaa kadi …ìe waajitoray…ìe kon ko yani e ma…ì…ìe …ìe anndi …óum ko immorde ka Alla!"
  9,127,"Si tawii Alla jippinii cortewol e Nulaa…óo Makko on (yo o his),jantiingol fiyaakuuji naafiquii…ìe …ìen, wo…ó…ìe e ma…ì…ìe ndaara wo…ó…ìe,…ìe wi'a : "Hara go…ó…óo no renti on?" Si go…ó…óo yi'aali …ìe,…ìe hibbito e jonnde nden. Anndee Alla surii …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen gaay e peewal e mo∆¥∆¥ere,O hoynii…ìe tawde ko …ìe yim…ìe …ìe faamataa."
  9,128,"Gom…óii arii e moo…óon, onon Aarabu'en, Nulaa…óo jeyaa…óo e moo…óon. Ko Aarabeejo wano mon. Hino sa…óta e makko ko sa…ótata e moo…óon, tii…óu…óo rer…óugol fewnugol on toppitoo fii mon. Kanko ko o heeroran…óo gom…óim…ìe …ìen neweende e yurmee- …óuu…óu…ói."
  9,129,"Si …ìe huccii ma …ìe gom…óinaali ma, maakan …ìe an Nulaa…óo: "Alla on Mo rewetee…óo nafaa woo alaa si wanaa Kanko on yonii lam. Ko e Makko mi fawii. Ko Kanko woni Senii…óo Jey…óo Arsi mawnu…óo on"."